User Story Title
AI Agent Confirms Successful Renewal and Sends Updated Policy Documents

User Story
As an AI agent,
I want to confirm the successful renewal and send the updated policy documents that include the new coverage changes,
So that the customer receives complete and accurate documentation of their renewed policy.

Acceptance Criteria

1. The AI agent shall confirm that the payment was successful and that the renewal is complete with the updated coverage.


2. The AI agent shall generate updated policy documents reflecting all coverage modifications.


3. The documents shall be sent to the customer via email and, if applicable, via postal mail.


4. The AI agent shall log the completion of the renewal process, including timestamps for all key steps.
